    • checkForNewCond

      private void checkForNewCond()
      Method to add an action to the button insertCond. The action on the Button will validate if all the fields have been filled and then will add a new ConditionJPanel

    • checkForRemCond

      private void checkForRemCond()
      Method to add an action to the button removeCond. The action on the button is responsible for removing the last ConditionJPanel inserted. It will also verify if the Condition can be remove, considering a Rule must have at least one condition
